title: Is this a video of the bikers on their way to Washington to support Brit Cavanaugh?
subtitle: According to Internet dwarves, bikers everywhere in the world are supporters of President Trump and often gather to support him.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A video showing the "Cyclists for Trump" group on their way to Washington, D.C., to support Brett Cavanaugh's confirmation hearing and demand Mr. Vincent's resignation.
